{"tid":421879,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日第二日返馬會 勁開心","createTime":"2017-10-02T15:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T12:37:39.000Z","uid":52764,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"22c01ebbd80815efebd3b9e4b3797e0c615bc5c1","tid":421879,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"尋日一返工 咁我就即刻上去聽CALL果度 <br />\n同上次差唔多 坐左一陣間有個組長姐姐叫我食飯先 <br />\n今次我學精左 <br />\n我用左十五分鐘就食晒D飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過返到去都仲有十五分鐘淨  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就返返去繼續聽CALL <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時全部食飯既同事得我一個返番個位度 <br />\n我覺得自己好勤力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我知道 食飯時間都係一樣會計人工 <br />\n所以響我能力之內 我都會一直做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論係咪BREAK緊都好 <br />\n我 的 字 典 裡 沒 有 蛇 王  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知道我返工 係全心全力為馬會做野 <br />\n所以我願意用盡我一切既力量為馬會為顧客提供最好既服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n無論係精神上 力度上 我都會盡力 <br />\n所以我入緊飛既時候 我一定會大大聲覆飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去證明我係用左一切既力量 為大家為馬會為顧客做到最好 <br />\n因為我相信 只要人地見到我盡力 咁搏命 訓晒身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地一定會見到既  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋就算就開跑 唔知賣唔賣得切 <br />\n我都會用最快既速度去覆飛  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我希望成為馬會最好既電話投注員工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都希望可以攞到85%勤工獎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我會盡力 亦都解釋到點解我咁憎人地蛇王 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n不過始終我都會尿急 <br />\n所以我都去左一次廁所 <br />\n本身我諗住去完就返 <br />\n不過我見到有個O靚仔(印象中係上次MON我果個哥哥個FD) <br />\n佢一路屙尿一路玩電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就即刻叫響廁所門口同人吹緊水個組長哥哥出黎  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同佢講: 有人響廁所入面玩電話呀!!!!!!!!!!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就即刻入去廁所 同我一齊的左個O靚仔出黎 <br />\n我見到個O靚仔同埋佢D FD即刻啤住我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n響佢地既眼神中 我FEEL到佢地想講 <br />\n&quot;死傻仔我屌你老母&quot;  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我好開心 因為我最憎人蛇王 仲要玩埋電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n返馬會唔係要盡力工作咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尾二果場同最後果場隔35分鐘 <br />\n見到我自己果組同埋左手面果兩組 <br />\n好多人走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n所以就即刻搵組長 <br />\n最後佢地全部俾組長話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n有一個C9仲要係咁同人講個新仔又幾ON9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地唔知道我呢個正義使者響背後出左幾多力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我希望令佢地明白 馬會係工作地方 <br />\n唔係娛樂場所 唔係去BALL 不停搵人吹水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n仲有 果陣好多人入左紙 就想話早走<br />\n我捉住果個後生同事 <br />\n我問佢: 點解你早走? 你唔使理同事同埋顧客既感受?<br />\n佢就話: 你都痴閪線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同佢講: 幫到廣大市民同埋馬迷落注 係我既光榮 你真係冇得救 根本就唔識乜野叫敬業樂業 點出黎做野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢即刻想作勢打鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗 你講粗口都算啦 仲要用暴力<br />\n咁我同個主任投訴 佢都叫個傻仔下次唔好咁早走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n差d講漏左 食飯果陣見到有個阿叔開馬會APPS<br />\n我即刻同組長報串<br />\n好似話佢俾人炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到收工 冇人再敢未拍卡入廁所 <br />\n我FEEL到我已取得階段性勝利了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到屋企 話返晒D野俾DADDY MAMMY聽 <br />\n佢地叫我俾D掌聲自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n點都好 返馬會 咪又係返工 <br />\n做野賣命係天經地義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我 冇 做 錯 到!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm